summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twelfth Avenue West from West Garfield Street to West Howe Street in the City of Seattle., by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 23891, creating Local Improvement District No. 2309 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
